msgid "Start"
msgstr "开始使用"

msgid "Learn"
msgstr "学习"

msgid "Features"
msgstr "特色功能"

msgid "Develop"
msgstr "开发"

msgid "Deploy and operate"
msgstr "部署与运维"

msgid "Reference"
msgstr "参考"

msgid "Internals and contribute"
msgstr "内部机制与贡献"

msgid ""
"Klein for Ray documentation for building stateful batch and streaming "
"dataflows on Ray."
msgstr "Klein for Ray 文档：在 Ray 上构建有状态批处理与流式数据流。"

msgid "Klein for Ray: Stateful stream processing on Ray"
msgstr "Klein for Ray：基于 Ray 的有状态流处理"

msgid ""
"Klein for Ray is a stateful stream processing library built on Ray. Use "
"the `DataStream` API to run bounded Ray Data inputs and long-running "
"streaming inputs with event time, managed keyed state, checkpoint "
"recovery, and SQL and Table APIs."
msgstr ""
"Klein for Ray 是一个构建于 Ray 之上的有状态流处理库。使用 `DataStream` API，可以运行有界 Ray Data "
"输入和长时间运行的流式输入，并获得事件时间、托管键控状态、检查点恢复以及 SQL 和 Table API 支持。"

msgid ""
"Klein for Ray is independent alpha software. It is not affiliated with, "
"endorsed by, or maintained by the Ray project."
msgstr "Klein for Ray 是独立开发的 alpha 阶段软件，与 Ray 项目没有隶属关系，也未获得其认可或由其维护。"

msgid "When should you use Klein?"
msgstr "何时应使用 Klein？"

msgid ""
"Use Klein when a Ray application needs long-running, record-oriented "
"processing and state that survives task failures or parallelism changes. "
"Klein provides event-time windows, interval joins, state time-to-live "
"(TTL), durable checkpoints, and idle-input-aware watermarks."
msgstr ""
"当 Ray 应用需要面向记录的长时间运行处理，并要求状态在任务故障或并行度变化后仍能保留时，可使用 Klein。Klein "
"提供事件时间窗口、区间连接、状态生存时间 (TTL)、持久检查点以及能感知空闲输入的水位线。"

msgid ""
"Use [Ray Data](https://docs.ray.io/en/latest/data/data.html) directly "
"when a workload is bounded, its operations are supported by Ray Data, and"
" it doesn't need streaming state or event-time progress. Klein delegates "
"compatible bounded execution to Ray Data instead of implementing another "
"batch engine."
msgstr ""
"当工作负载有界、其操作受 Ray Data 支持，且不需要流式状态或事件时间推进时，请直接"
"使用 [Ray Data](https://docs.ray.io/en/latest/data/data.html)。Klein 将兼容的有界执行"
"委托给 Ray Data，而不是另行实现一个批处理引擎。"

msgid "Install Klein"
msgstr "安装 Klein"

msgid ""
"Klein for Ray targets Python 3.10 through 3.12 and Ray 2.56.x "
"(`ray[data]>=2.56.1,<2.57`). Install the project from this checkout:"
msgstr ""
"Klein for Ray 面向 Python 3.10 至 3.12 和 Ray "
"2.56.x（`ray[data]>=2.56.1,<2.57`）。请从当前检出版本安装项目："

msgid ""
"See the complete [installation guide](installation.md) for optional "
"extras, cluster environment checks, verification, upgrades, and "
"troubleshooting. Read [Compatibility](compatibility.md) before changing "
"the Ray dependency range."
msgstr ""
"完整的[安装指南](installation.md)介绍可选依赖、集群环境检查、验证、升级和故障排查。更改 Ray "
"依赖版本范围前，请阅读[兼容性](compatibility.md)。"

msgid "Learn Klein"
msgstr "学习 Klein"

msgid "Getting started"
msgstr "快速入门"

msgid ""
"Build and run your first bounded pipeline, then learn how to submit a "
"streaming job."
msgstr "构建并运行第一个有界管道，然后学习如何提交流式作业。"

msgid "Key concepts"
msgstr "核心概念"

msgid ""
"Learn how Klein represents a dataflow, chooses an execution mode, tracks "
"event time, and recovers state."
msgstr "了解 Klein 如何表示数据流、选择执行模式、跟踪事件时间以及恢复状态。"

msgid "Feature highlights"
msgstr "特色功能"

msgid ""
"Compare hybrid execution, state, event time, continuous SQL, checkpoint-"
"aware outputs, live rescaling, detached jobs, and Ray Serve integration."
msgstr "对比混合执行、状态、事件时间、持续 SQL、检查点感知输出、在线扩缩容、detached 作业和 Ray Serve 集成。"

msgid "Architecture"
msgstr "架构"

msgid ""
"Follow a graph from public APIs through planning, Ray Data or streaming "
"actors, ordered transport, checkpoints, and recovery."
msgstr "跟随一张图，了解它如何从公共 API 经过规划、Ray Data 或流式 actor、有序传输、检查点，直至恢复。"

msgid "User guides"
msgstr "用户指南"

msgid ""
"Configure jobs, use Ray Data and SQL, manage state, store checkpoints, "
"and operate pipelines."
msgstr "配置作业、使用 Ray Data 和 SQL、管理状态、存储检查点并运维管道。"

msgid "DataStream programming"
msgstr "DataStream 编程"

msgid ""
"Choose row or batch functions, manage callable lifecycles, preserve "
"ordering, and design serializable, observable user code."
msgstr "选择逐行或批量函数，管理可调用对象生命周期，保持顺序，并设计可序列化、可观测的用户代码。"

msgid "Production walkthrough"
msgstr "生产环境实战"

msgid ""
"Build, observe, stop, and restore a Kafka pipeline with event-time state "
"and checkpoint-transactional output."
msgstr "构建、观测、停止和恢复一个具有事件时间状态及检查点事务型输出的 Kafka 管道。"

msgid "Production readiness"
msgstr "生产就绪"

msgid ""
"Verify compatibility, recovery, delivery, capacity, observability, "
"security, and rollback before a launch."
msgstr "上线前验证兼容性、恢复、交付、容量、可观测性、安全性和回滚能力。"

msgid "Connector catalog"
msgstr "连接器目录"

msgid ""
"Choose inputs and outputs, then review every option, default, schema, "
"execution mode, and delivery guarantee."
msgstr "选择输入和输出，然后查看每个选项、默认值、模式、执行模式和交付保证。"

msgid "API reference"
msgstr "API 参考"

msgid "Find public classes, functions, methods, and configuration options."
msgstr "查找公共类、函数、方法和配置选项。"

msgid "Limits and stability"
msgstr "限制与稳定性"

msgid ""
"Review unsupported combinations, non-goals, API stability, and alpha "
"upgrade boundaries before committing to an architecture."
msgstr "确定架构前，审阅不支持的组合、非目标、API 稳定性和 alpha 阶段的升级边界。"

msgid "Explore features"
msgstr "探索特色功能"

msgid "Hybrid Ray execution"
msgstr "Ray 混合执行"

msgid ""
"Use one lazy graph with Ray Data lowering for compatible bounded work and"
" native Ray Core operators for continuous or streaming-only work."
msgstr "使用同一张惰性图：兼容的有界工作负载降低为 Ray Data，持续或仅支持流式处理的工作负载则使用原生 Ray Core 算子。"

msgid "Managed state and event time"
msgstr "托管状态与事件时间"

msgid ""
"Use keyed state, TTL, timers, key groups, checkpoint restore, and idle-"
"aware watermarks; continue into the event-time guide for windows and "
"joins."
msgstr "使用键控状态、TTL、定时器、键组、检查点恢复和空闲感知水位线；有关窗口和连接，请继续阅读事件时间指南。"

msgid "Continuous SQL and tables"
msgstr "持续 SQL 与表"

msgid ""
"Run bounded or continuous SQL, work with explicit changelog rows, and "
"define connector tables with DDL."
msgstr "运行有界或持续 SQL、处理显式变更日志行，并使用 DDL 定义连接器表。"

msgid "Checkpoint-aware output"
msgstr "检查点感知输出"

msgid ""
"Understand how source progress, state, replay, and transactional sink "
"publication compose into an end-to-end guarantee."
msgstr "了解源进度、状态、重放和事务型 sink 发布如何共同构成端到端保证。"

msgid "Live operator rescaling"
msgstr "在线算子扩缩容"

msgid ""
"Resize a supported running streaming operator through a checkpoint-"
"coordinated topology change."
msgstr "通过检查点协调的拓扑变更，调整受支持的运行中流式算子的并行度。"

msgid "Driver-independent jobs"
msgstr "独立于 driver 的作业"

msgid ""
"Keep detached streaming jobs alive after the submitting driver exits, "
"then reattach, observe, cancel, or recover them explicitly."
msgstr "提交作业的 driver 退出后，仍保持 detached 流式作业运行；随后可显式重新附加、观测、取消或恢复作业。"

msgid "Ray Serve execution regions"
msgstr "Ray Serve 执行区域"

msgid ""
"Move an eligible transform chain behind an independently deployed Ray "
"Serve endpoint and review its retry and checkpoint boundary."
msgstr "通过独立部署的 Ray Serve 端点运行符合条件的转换链，并检查其重试和检查点边界。"

msgid "Feature boundaries"
msgstr "功能边界"

msgid ""
"Check execution-mode, connector, recovery, scaling, and alpha-"
"compatibility limits before choosing an architecture."
msgstr "选择架构前，请检查执行模式、连接器、恢复、扩缩容和 alpha 兼容性限制。"

msgid "How does Klein use Ray?"
msgstr "Klein 如何使用 Ray？"

msgid ""
"In `auto` mode, Klein compiles a fully batch-lowerable bounded dataflow "
"to Ray Data operations when `udf.ignore-exception=false`. An unbounded "
"source, a streaming-only vertex, or the record-level ignore-exception "
"policy selects long-lived operators on Ray Core. Those operators store "
"records in ordered micro-batches. When enabled, Ray's Object Store can "
"cache sufficiently large immutable checkpoint fragments, while external "
"storage provides the durable recovery boundary."
msgstr ""
"在 `auto` 模式下，当 `udf.ignore-exception=false` 时，Klein 会将可完全降低为批处理的"
"有界数据流编译为 Ray Data 操作。无界数据源、仅支持流式处理的顶点或记录级忽略异常"
"策略，会让作业选择 Ray Core 上的长生命周期算子。这些算子以有序微批存储记录。启用"
"缓存后，Ray Object Store 可缓存达到大小阈值的不可变检查点片段；外部存储则提供持久"
"恢复边界。"

msgid ""
"Klein's distribution contributes the `ray.klein` namespace package. It "
"doesn't install or replace Ray's `ray/__init__.py`, which keeps the "
"source tree compatible with a future move into the Ray repository."
msgstr ""
"Klein 发行包提供 `ray.klein` 命名空间包。它不会安装或替换 Ray 的 "
"`ray/__init__.py`，从而使源代码树能够兼容未来迁入 Ray 仓库的计划。"

msgid "Get help and contribute"
msgstr "获取帮助与参与贡献"

msgid ""
"Start with the [FAQ](faq.md) and [troubleshooting "
"guide](troubleshooting.md). For project support channels and the "
"information to include, see the [support policy](https://github.com"
"/yuchen-ecnu/klein/blob/main/SUPPORT.md). Read the [contribution "
"guide](https://github.com/yuchen-ecnu/klein/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md) "
"before changing public APIs or runtime behavior. Use the process in the "
"[security policy](https://github.com/yuchen-"
"ecnu/klein/blob/main/SECURITY.md) to report a vulnerability."
msgstr ""
"请先查看 [FAQ](faq.md) "
"和[故障排查指南](troubleshooting.md)。项目支持渠道及求助时需提供的信息见[支持策略](https://github.com"
"/yuchen-ecnu/klein/blob/main/SUPPORT.md)。更改公共 API "
"或运行时行为前，请阅读[贡献指南](https://github.com/yuchen-"
"ecnu/klein/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md)。报告漏洞时，请遵循[安全策略](https://github.com"
"/yuchen-ecnu/klein/blob/main/SECURITY.md) 中的流程。"

